title: Dusek Sets Program Record in Five Set Win over Auburn (University of Kentucky)
text: ( Source : University of Kentucky ) Box Score (pdf) AUBURN, Ala. - The No. 20 Kentucky Wildcat volleyball team battled a full five sets en route to its ninth consecutive win, taking down the Auburn Tigers , 3-2 (22-25, 25-22, 23-25, 25-21,
